{"tid":954863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《Red Dead Redemption 2》玩家和女友親熱時　因這原因不幸分手","createTime":"2018-12-25T03:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T03:23:52.000Z","uid":212399,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"57af59b36fc92436f2e081a3a52dfb03f5ca11e6","tid":954863,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T03:22:43.000Z","msg":"《Red Dead Redemption 2》遊戲對范德林幫中每個主要角色的刻畫都很細緻，導致了不光光是天下無敵的亞瑟摩根，其他的成員也一樣魅力非凡。在《Red Dead Redemption 2》的Facebook群組中，就有人自曝稱自己太過於迷戀遊戲中的Sadie Adler，導致在一次親熱中喊錯名稱而和女朋友鬧分手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201812/22/vva1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201812%2F22%2Fvva1.jpg&h=1040af64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSadie Adler是《Red Dead Redemption 2》中女性陣營的傑出代表，受到廣大粉絲的喜愛。她是一位性格暴躁的寡婦，冷酷無情且不懼怕任何人。發誓要讓殺死她丈夫的人付出代價。雖然看起來很難相處，但她對於愛情的忠誠在那個年代彌足珍貴，展現了開展女權運動的時代獨立自強的女性標杆。不光光她在遊戲中狂野的顏值，性感的口音，甚至有些時候爆表的戰鬥力，顯然令屏幕另一邊的玩家蠢蠢欲動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/31435/Red-Dead-Redemption-2-player-broke-up\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F31435%2FRed-Dead-Redemption-2-player-broke-up&d=HoDbkrHw8ewrkyQVt6SJ5xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6df62da9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/31435/Red-Dead-Redemption-2-player-broke-up</a>"},{"pid":"927ba0c51ebe5f71918518c27a019fd2aa32074e","tid":954863,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T03:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafdff94fc087cee9cebe309a4f579518d72dd6b","tid":954863,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}